snippet.textDisplay: Wonderful. This is peak of the fusion. A lovely combo of Sindhi and Punjabi remix of two of the subcontinent's best ever Sufi poets. This song is a lesson on fate and fortune and how loves leads to the jogi trails. I wish coke studio Pakistan could come up with this standard of poetry and melodies fusion where heart beats with guitar and every bit feels like a divine verse to dip deep into the whirlpool of the mystic thoughts. Love.
